text: Frank Jordan (born 1935) is an American politician who served as the 40th mayor of San Francisco, California. Frank Jordan may also refer to: *Frank Jordan (cricketer) (1905–1995) *Frank Jordan (footballer) (1883–1938) *Frank Jordan (water polo) (1932–2012) *Frank C. Jordan (died 1940), 20th Secretary of State of California *Frank M. Jordan (1888–1970), 22nd Secretary of State of California * Frank Jordan (American football) (1897–1980), American football player
